the first and best of the `` return to 'nam to get p.o.w . 's '' movies this action classic has gene hackman as a former marine who is still looking for his son who was taken prisoner in 'nam in the 70 's . with a great supporting cast ( robert stack , fred ward patrick swayze , reb brown , and more ) he set out to bring his son home . great action in the final 40 mins . and really just a slam bang action movie ! !